WEBVTT

00:04.883 --> 00:09.083
Kyary's name is now synonymous with the top of Japanese pop.

00:09.400 --> 00:14.497
Her quirky unique style in music and fashion has brought this 21-year-old Harajuku girl...

00:14.738 --> 00:16.247
...onto the world stage.

00:19.703 --> 00:24.440
With her world tour hitting Australia this month, when she's not singing or performing,...

00:24.660 --> 00:27.577
...she's a model, actress, author and businesswoman.

00:27.800 --> 00:31.401
Kyary's conquering the world one fashion monster at a time.

